00:13:09,096 --> 00:13:11,036
Di “mamá”.

107
00:13:14,736 --> 00:13:15,856
Mamá.

108
00:13:17,376 --> 00:13:18,566
Papa.

109
00:13:34,446 --> 00:13:36,366
Besa al bebé por mí.

110
00:13:59,526 --> 00:14:02,506
- Okay. Okay. Okay.
